text: Codex Guelferbytanus may refer to: *Codex Guelferbytanus A *Codex Guelferbytanus B *Codex Guelferbytanus 64 Weissenburgensis, which contains in the lower text of the palimpsests: Codex Guelferbytanus A, Codex Guelferbytanus B, and Codex Carolinus. Category:Herzog August Library
title: Codex Guelferbytanus
